00:16:10,860 --> 00:16:11,440
And so,

407
00:16:11,440 --> 00:16:12,660
we want to,

408
00:16:12,700 --> 00:16:14,260
we start by assuming

409
00:16:15,180 --> 00:16:18,100
that we can make an expansion in a small parameter.

410
00:16:18,320 --> 00:16:19,360
We make the expansion,

411
00:16:19,360 --> 00:16:20,800
mathematically expand,

412
00:16:21,220 --> 00:16:24,800
and then check whether the corrections to the first term

413
00:16:24,800 --> 00:16:26,520
are big enough,

